{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Your task is to write the text for our 'Everything Included' section. For each feature listed below, provide a bolded Headline and a single, benefit-focused Description.
    
    The tone should be reassuring, premium, and trustworthy.
    
    Features:
    
    High-Quality Prescription Lenses
    
    Durable & Lightweight Polycarbonate Lenses
    
    Essential Protective Coatings (Anti-reflective, scratch-resistant, UV-blocking)
    
    Free UK Shipping
    
    60-Day Hassle-Free Returns
    
    1-Year Scratch Guarantee"
    
    Prompt 2: Generating the Liquid/HTML Code for the Value Props
    Once you have the text from Prompt 1, use it in this next prompt to get the code.
    
    Your Prompt to Shopify AI:
    
    "You are a Shopify theme developer. Your task is to generate a Liquid and HTML code block for a list of features.
    
    Instructions:
    
    Create an unordered list (<ul>).
    
    Each list item (<li>) must contain an icon <img> and a <div> with a <strong> headline and a <p> description.
    
    The icon's src must use the Shopify Liquid asset_url filter. Use placeholder icon names like icon-lenses.svg, icon-shield.svg, etc.
    
    Now, create this structure using the following text:
    
    (Here, you will copy and paste the headlines and descriptions generated by the AI in Prompt 1)
    
    Example Text:
    
    Headline: High-Quality Prescription Lenses
    
    Description: Your choice of single-vision, readers, or non-prescription lenses are included.
    
    Headline: Durable & Lightweight Lenses
    
    Description: We use polycarbonate as standard—a lightweight, impact-resistant material.
    
    (...and so on for the rest of the features)"
    
    Prompt 3: Generating the CSS Code
    Once the AI gives you the HTML block from Prompt 2, you'll use that code to get the correct styling.
    
    Your Prompt to Shopify AI:
    
    "You are a front-end developer specializing in CSS. Write the CSS to style the following HTML block.
    
    HTML to Style:
    (Paste the full <ul>...</ul> block that the AI generated in Prompt 2 here)
    
    Styling requirements:
    
    The list should have no bullet points.
    
    There should be a 25px gap between each list item., add brief description of a product too  and use brand colours in this entire block  
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-everything-included-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding_top }}px 0 {{ block.settings.section_padding_bottom }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
  }

  .ai-everything-included-container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .ai-everything-included-header-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.header_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-everything-included-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.title_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.title_margin }}px;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.title_transform }};
  }

  .ai-everything-included-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtitle_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtitle_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.subtitle_margin }}px;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .ai-everything-included-product-info-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: {{ block.settings.product_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-everything-included-product-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.product_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.product_title_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.product_title_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.product_title_margin }}px;
  }

  .ai-everything-included-product-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.product_description_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.product_description_color }};
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .ai-everything-included-list-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax({{ block.settings.min_column_width }}px, 1fr));
    gap: {{ block.settings.item_spacing }}px;
  }

  .ai-everything-included-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: {{ block.settings.icon_text_spacing }}px;
    padding: {{ block.settings.item_padding }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.item_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.item_border_radius }}px;
    border: {{ block.settings.item_border_width }}px solid {{ block.settings.item_border_color }};
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  {% if block.settings.enable_hover_effect %}
    .ai-everything-included-item-{{ ai_gen_id }}:hover {
      transform: translateY(-{{ block.settings.hover_lift }}px);
      box-shadow: 0 {{ block.settings.hover_shadow_blur }}px {{ block.settings.hover_shadow_spread }}px rgba(167, 97, 17, {{ block.settings.hover_shadow_opacity | divided_by: 10.0 }});
      background-color: {{ block.settings.item_hover_background }};
      border-color: {{ block.settings.item_hover_border_color }};
    }
  {% endif %}

  .ai-everything-included-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size }}px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.icon_background }};
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.icon_border_radius }}px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 2px;
    border: 2px solid {{ block.settings.icon_border_color }};
  }

  .ai-everything-included-icon-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.6 }}px;
    height: {{ block.settings.icon_size | times: 0.6 }}px;
    fill: {{ block.settings.icon_color }};
  }

  .ai-everything-included-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .ai-everything-included-headline-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.headline_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.headline_weight }};
    color: {{ block.settings.headline_color }};
    margin: 0 0 {{ block.settings.headline_margin }}px;
    text-transform: {{ block.settings.headline_transform }};
  }

  .ai-everything-included-description-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.description_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.description_color }};
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 768px) {
    .ai-everything-included-list-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: {{ block.settings.item_spacing | times: 0.75 }}px;
    }

    .ai-everything-included-item-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.item_padding | times: 0.75 }}px;
    }

    .ai-everything-included-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
